		<div id="post_message_1304223">
                  
                  The Wii is like &quot;The American Idol&quot; of the consoles. The 360 amd PS3 are like the &quot;Firefly&quot;, &quot;Farscape&quot;, &quot;Dresden Files&quot;, etc. They offer more but cost more to produce and they are not mainstream.<br />
<br />
The average people don't know, don't care and don't have the technical knowledge to use all of the multiple extra features. They just want to pop a game in the system and have fun.
                  
